      "series_title": "MERCHANDISE TRANSFER ORDERS",
      "series_description": "Copies of the orders are sent to the Data Processing Division where information on the form is keyed into store inventory files, resulting in the creation of the Daily Merchandise Transfer Reports (series S-54-31). The reports should be retained until completion of one audit and the release of the audit report.",
      "legal_citation": null
    },
