      "trigger_desc": "Temporary Record. return of item property manager. ## Approval of Records Disposition Authority By signing this agreement, Alcoholic Beverage Control Board acknowledges its responsibilities in proper management of its records and agrees abide by implementation guidelines listed below: Alcoholic Beverage Control Board will designate a managerial position as agency records officer. position is responsible ensuring development of quality record keeping systems that meet business and legal needs of department, coordinating and destruction of records, and ensuring regular implementation of agency's approved RDA. Alcoholic Beverage Control Board agrees develop procedures regular implementation, document destruction of records, and submit a report on its records management activities State Records Commission in July of each year. Despite provisions of this authorization, no records may be destroyed that are necessary agency compliance with requirements of state Sunset Act, agency audit, and any legal notice, or subpoena. Alcoholic Beverage Control Board will make every effort maintain permanent records in a secure environment, in a usable order, and under environmental conditions that will ensure their continued preservation, while in custody of board. Alcoholic Beverage Control Board agrees allow State Records Commission, its staff, and Examiners of Public Accounts examine condition of permanent records maintained in custody of board and inspect documentation on destruction of public records. By: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_ Date: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_ Randall C. Smith, Administrator > Alcoholic Beverage Control Board By: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_ Date: \\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_\\_